Basic Genome assembly statistic tool to calculate Nx values e.g. N50, N10, NG50

INSTALLATION

a) Download git repository
b) Compile java classes
   # in gnx-tools folder run
   mkdir bin
   javac -d bin/ src/uk/ac/ebi/gnx/*
c) package jar file
   # in gnx-tools foder run
   ant -f package.xml
d) execute jar file
   java -jar nx.jar

DONE


